Package: footballR
Title: Functions for Football (Soccer) Data
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R: person("Aidan", "Boland", email = "aidansboland@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7649-5968"))
Description: This package contains football data for Premier League
     matches, and functions to manipulate and display the
     data. The most recent data can also be easily 
     downloaded using this package.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
